<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to Rental Management</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
        .header { background: #007bff; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; }
        .content { padding: 20px; background: #f9f9f9; }
        .button { display: inline-block; padding: 12px 24px; background: #007bff; color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px; margin: 10px 0; }
        .footer { text-align: center; padding: 20px; color: #666; font-size: 12px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Welcome to Leazo!</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <h2>Hi {{firstName}},</h2>
            <p>Welcome to our rental platform! We're excited to have you on board.</p>
            <p>Your account has been created successfully and you can now start exploring our wide range of rental products.</p>
            <p>Here's what you can do:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Browse our product catalog</li>
                <li>Check availability and make bookings</li>
                <li>Track your rental orders</li>
                <li>Leave reviews for products you've rented</li>
            </ul>
            <p>
                <a href="{{loginUrl}}" class="button">Start Exploring</a>
            </p>
            <p>If you have any questions, feel free to contact our support team.</p>
            <p>Best regards,<br>The Rental Management Team</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; 2024 Rental Management. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>